# Bug Bounty & Red Team — Tools Command Reference (Part 3 — Mobile, SMB, OSINT, Wordlists)

> Final batch. Covers Android mobile pentesting (relevant to your personal Vivo test device), SMB/Windows enumeration, OSINT username/email lookup, wordlist generation, and general-purpose web scanners.

