## 3. General Web Vulnerability Scanners

### Nikto
```bash
nikto -h https://target.com
nikto -h https://target.com -Tuning 1,2,3            # specific test categories
```

### Wapiti
```bash
wapiti -u https://target.com
```

### ZAP (OWASP ZAP — CLI mode)
```bash
zap-cli quick-scan --self-contained https://target.com
zap-baseline.py -t https://target.com                 # docker baseline scan
```

