## 4. OSINT — Username / Email / Person Lookup

### Sherlock (username across platforms)
```bash
python3 sherlock.py username123
```

### theHarvester (already in Part 1 — email/subdomain OSINT)
```bash
theHarvester -d target.com -b all
```

### Recon-ng (modular OSINT framework)
```bash
recon-ng
marketplace install all
workspaces create target_workspace
```

### Holehe (check if email registered on platforms)
```bash
holehe email@example.com
```

