## 5. Wordlist Generation / Management

### CeWL (crawl target site to build custom wordlist)
```bash
cewl https://target.com -d 2 -m 5 -w custom_wordlist.txt
```

### Crunch (pattern-based wordlist generation)
```bash
crunch 8 8 -t @@@@%%%% -o wordlist.txt                # 8-char pattern
crunch 6 10 0123456789 -o numeric_wordlist.txt
```

### Hashcat rules (mutate existing wordlist — combine with hashcat)
```bash
hashcat -m 0 -a 0 hash.txt rockyou.txt -r rules/best64.rule
```

