## 6. DNS Deep Recon

### dnsrecon
```bash
dnsrecon -d target.com -a
```

### fierce
```bash
fierce --domain target.com
```

### dig / host (built-in, quick checks)
```bash
dig target.com ANY
dig target.com MX
host -t TXT target.com
```

