## 7. Screenshot + Recon Combo

### Aquatone
```bash
cat live_hosts.txt | aquatone -out aquatone_report/
```

### Photon (fast crawler, extracts emails/keys/subdomains from a site)
```bash
python3 photon.py -u https://target.com -o photon_output
```

