## Is This Everything?

Realistically — haan, ab tumhare paas **60+ tools** cover ho chuke hain teeno parts mein. Ye industry-standard toolkit hai jo professional bug bounty hunters aur red teamers use karte hain. Isse zyada tools add karna diminishing returns hoga — is point ke baad focus **tools install karne** se zyada **inhe deeply master karna** (Phase 2 roadmap) aur **practically apply karna** authorized targets pe hona chahiye.

**Reminder:** Roadmap ke hisaab se abhi Phase 1 (Web Caching + JWT) hi incomplete hai — teeno parts ke tools install/practice Phase 2 mein systematically karna, ek-ek karke, jaldi mein sab install mat karna.
